    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "I tested this plugin here which works for search and replace: https://github.com/ipython-contrib/IPython-notebook-extensions/blob/master/usability/search.js\n\nCtrl-F for seach, Ctrl-Shift-F for search and replace, this works but the cursor isn't reported which makes this very hard to use.\n\nThis can be added to the plugin to get a nice dialog:\n// require(['/static/components/codemirror/addon/dialog/dialog.js']);\n// require(['/static/components/codemirror/addon/dialog/dialog.css']);\n\nBut I guess the dialog should be displayed in a fixed position (near the menu bar) so the interface always is visible when doing the search and replace.\n"
  },
