    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "I have also found myself wanting robust search and replace capability. It sounds like this should wait until #6257 is resolved, as `dockable` sounds really clutch... if not for the initial interface revealed when doing Ctrl+F, then certainly for all the other kinds of things that a search can do.\n\nWould a Backbone implementation be welcome, or should something in the current style (vanilla + jquery) be used?\n\nHere are some brainstormed things:\nhttps://gist.github.com/bollwyvl/2477d23debbe688f7dbe\n"
